What does an Odoo Functional Consultant do?

They don't primarily write code. Instead, they:

Meet clients and understand their business.
Analyze existing business processes.
Recommend how Odoo can solve their problems.
Configure Odoo modules.
Train employees to use Odoo.
Test the ERP system before deployment.
Support users after implementation.

Think of them as the bridge between the client and the technical developers.

