4. Requirement Gathering ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

Learn to ask clients questions such as:

What is your business?
How many employees?
How many branches?
Current software?
What problems are you facing?
What reports do you need?
Which departments will use Odoo?

Then prepare a document listing the requirements.

5. Business Analysis ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

Since you already have an MBA, this is a strength.

