10. Basic Technical Knowledge (Recommended)

You don't need to become a full developer, but understanding these topics will help:

Python basics
PostgreSQL basics
XML basics
Odoo Models
Odoo Views
Odoo ORM (basic concepts)

This allows you to communicate effectively with developers.

