You are in a strong position to become a Functional + Technical Consultant. This combination is highly valued because you can both understand business requirements and collaborate effectively with developers.

I recommend this roadmap for you
First: Complete your current Odoo Technical course.
Then: Learn the functional side module by module using real business scenarios.
Finally: Build 5–10 complete ERP implementation case studies and publish them on GitHub and LinkedIn.

That combination will make your profile much stronger than focusing only on coding or only on business.
